Class LoggingStoreDecorator

  • java.lang.Object
    • fr.inria.atlanmod.neoemf.data.store.AbstractPersistentStore

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    PersistentStore, InternalEObject.EStore

    public class LoggingStoreDecorator
extends AbstractPersistentStoreDecorator
    A PersistentStore wrapper that logs every call to its methods in the NeoLogger.
